		"excerpt": "Over the last two days, Cloudflare observed two events that had effects on global Internet traffic levels. Cloudflare handles approximately 10% of all Internet requests, so we have significant visibility into traffic from countries and networks across the world.",
		"feature_image": "http://blog.cloudflare.com/content/images/2017/09/iss053e002392.jpg",
		"feature_image_alt": null,
